

This page lists all the relevant formats for the wiki mode.


  - Paragraphs begins at column 0.
  - Four or more hyphens creates a horizontal line.
  - A hyphen list such as this creates a bullet list.
  - 1. Creates a numbered list.
  - Indent with one or more spaces to use monospace.
  - Italics *italics* or empasis.
  - Bold **bold** or strong emphais.
  - Bold-italics ***bold-italics*** very strong emphasis.
  - Underlined _underlined_.
  - Verbatim text is this =verbatim=.
  - WikiFormat#Headings Headings
  - WikiFormat#Tables Tables
  - WikiFormat#Lisp Lisp

  - WikiFill

----
			  This is centered text.
			  And this follows.
----


